description: Alexa asks you a series of questions and you answer with "yes" and "no". Based on your answers Alexa finds out which board game suits you the most. You can also ask Alexa to tell you more about the game she found out for you and she will describe the game in further details. This game is based on the popular internet board-game decider chart.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, open find my board game
name: Find My Board Game
shortDescription: Alexa helps you find out which board game you like the most.
